body:
Map absolute paths to posix textFiles keys in archive extract (fixes
prepareFromArchive on Win32). Normalize missing targetDisplayPath slashes;
align segment write plan test with logical posix absolute paths.

Update public docs and maintainer maps for orchestrated typecheck/build,
@i18nprune/report-schema vs @i18nprune/report SPA workspace names, and
apps/web domain-folder layout after the refactor.

Split upload flags onto `share upload` so delete can take --project <id>.
Wire --debug-cache on list/view/delete via shared cache debug helper;
improve empty-cache hints and heal/backup warnings for share.json.

Introduce systems/health.md for typecheck, test, knip, and madge commands;
keep knip.json ignore rationale in systems/knip.md. Trim architecture §8
to point at the new hub.

Replace dynamic @shikijs/* import() with top-level imports in extension webview
and landing highlighters. Drop shiki ignore rules from knip.json; keep
@cloudflare/workers-types ignored for og.svg.ts triple-slash reference.

Add tests/fixtures/layout-* mini-apps and CLI integration coverage for
locale_per_dir and feature_bundle; document all three layouts in docs/locales/layouts.md;
remove stale meta sidecars and locales edit docs; refresh generate parity snapshot.
